<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Student Achievement Management</title>
    <style>
   
body {
    margin: 0;
    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    scroll-behavior: smooth;
}

.hero-section {
    display: flex;
    height: 100vh;
    background: #4b95f4;
    color: white;
}

.text-container {
    flex: 1;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 0 50px;
}

.text-container h1 {
    font-size: 3em;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
}

.text-container p {
    font-size: 1.2em;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
}

.buttons {
    display: flex;
    gap: 15px;
}

.btn {
    padding: 10px 20px;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: white;
    border-radius: 5px;
    font-weight: bold;
    text-align: center;
    display: inline-block;
}

.learn-more {
    background-color: orange;
    
}

.learn-more:hover {
  background-color: white;
  color: orange;
}

.login {
    background-color: transparent;
    border: 2px solid white;
}

.login:hover {
  background-color: white;
  color: #4b95f4;
}

.image-container {
    flex: 1;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    overflow: hidden; 
}

.image-container img {
    width: 100%; 
    height: 100%; 
    object-fit: cover; 
    max-width: 100%; 
}

.summary-section {
    padding: 50px;
    background: #f5f5f5;
    text-align: center;
}

.summary-section h2 {
    font-size: 2em;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
}

.summary-section p {
    font-size: 1.2em;
    max-width: 1000px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    line-height: 1.5;
}

    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="hero-section">
        <div class="text-container">
            <h1>Student Achievement Management System</h1>
            <p>Effortlessly track and manage Student Achievements</p>
            <div class="buttons">
                <a href="#summary" class="btn learn-more">Learn More</a>
                <a href="/loginpage" class="btn login">Login</a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="image-container">
            <img src="/home_achieve.jpg">
        </div>
    </div>
    <section id="summary" class="summary-section">
        <h2>About the System</h2>
        <p>Student Achievement Management System (S.A.M.S)  is a web-based platform that aims to facilitate the tracking and
          management of student achievement data. S.A.M.S allows students to manage their event
          participation and accomplishments such as academic, extracurricular, and personal
          achievements. Additionally, the students are assigned a regular or representative account where
          representative accounts designated by the teachers have the ability to share notifications about
          upcoming events.</p><br>
          <p> S.A.M.S provides teachers acting as administrators with the ability to manage student data
          and export data based on customized filters. The system allows for efficient tracking of student
          achievement data promotes engagement among students and encourages them to take part in
          events. </p>
    </section>
    <script>
      document.querySelector('.learn-more').addEventListener('click', function (e) {
          e.preventDefault(); 
          document.querySelector('#summary').scrollIntoView({
              behavior: 'smooth',
              block: 'start'
          });
      });
  </script>
  
</body>
</html>
